但係一開group就變質咁 覺唔覺 不過你開我會想入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無打算開呀，我所有心事都係自己諗自己消化<br />\n不過成日做人垃圾桶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35bdfa9c0f0d647c38e479c8f52b40d65f2b94ae","tid":486763,"uid":122976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T09:41:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>開個gp比同路巴打一齊傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n 我明喺度講唔到太多私人嘢 但係一開group就變質咁 覺唔覺 不過你開我會想入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無打算開呀，我所有心事都係自己諗自己消化<br />\n不過成日做人垃圾桶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所有心事都自己解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實有時係想有多個意見 睇法 其他人會點面對咁"},{"pid":"42482f41379949b9e8010e0fe8c2af0e913368d1","tid":486763,"uid":151337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T09:52:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同病相連<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當認識到身邊既朋友點對自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點對你？ 你一認真講嘢就唔理你？ 我認真講嘢無人理 講無營養廢話就應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有理過下既, 普遍都會俾下feedback, <br />\n但覺得想食花生多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}